  "_comment": "ROCKE-owned architecture SSOT. Hardware facts only (no pipeline/scheduler vocabulary). MFMA atom sets are hardware-verified on real hardware (see dsl_docs/architecture/multi_arch_data_layout.md). Each MMA row: {family,a,b,c,m,n,k,op_id}; op_id is the opaque backend handle (matches IRBuilder.mfma_* today).",
