    "gfx1201": {
      "_comment": "RDNA4 (Navi 48). WAVE32, WMMA not MFMA. Datalayout/triple inherited from RDNA3 backend (RDNA buffer SRD word3 0x31014000 + contiguous gfx11 waitcnt). WMMA 16x16x16 ABI differs from gfx11: NO cross-half operand duplication, A/B are <8 x half> per lane (intrinsic v8f16/v8i16), builtin __builtin_amdgcn_wmma_f32_16x16x16_f16_w32_gfx12; output column-distributed acc[j]=matrix[(lane/16)*8+j][lane%16]. Lane maps HYPOTHESIS — verify with examples/gfx1201/wmma_probe.py before trusting matmul_nbits.",
      "family": "rdna",
      "target_family": "gfx12_rdna",
      "wave_size": 32,
      "lds_capacity_bytes": 65536,
      "vmcnt_bits": 6,
      "memory": {
        "has_async_lds": false,
        "has_ds_read_tr": false,
        "buffer_load_max_dwords": 4
      },
      "limits": {
        "max_threads_per_block": 1024,
        "vgprs": 256,
        "agprs": 0,
        "sgprs": 106
      },
      "mma": [
        {"family": "wmma", "a": "fp16", "b": "fp16", "c": "fp32", "m": 16, "n": 16, "k": 16, "op_id": "wmma_gfx12_f32_16x16x16_f16"},
        {"family": "wmma", "a": "bf16", "b": "bf16", "c": "fp32", "m": 16, "n": 16, "k": 16, "op_id": "wmma_gfx12_f32_16x16x16_bf16"}
      ]
    },
    "gfx1250": {
      "_comment": "gfx1250-class CDNA multi-chip device on the GFX12 programming model (wave32, WMMA, no MFMA). Primary fp16/bf16 WMMA atom is 16x16x32 (NOT gfx1201's 16x16x16). ABI empirically confirmed on ROCm 7.13 clang 23 (gfx1250 device target): __builtin_amdgcn_wmma_f32_16x16x32_f16 -> llvm.amdgcn.wmma.f32.16x16x32.f16.v8f32.v16f16(i1,<16 x half>,i1,<16 x half>,i16,<8 x float>,i1,i1); bf16 uses v16bf16 (<16 x bfloat>) directly, not the gfx11 <16 x i16> bitcast. Datalayout/triple byte-identical to gfx950/gfx1201. This catalog ships only the validated fp16/bf16 and fp8/bf8 WMMA atoms; block-scaled F4/block16 forms are intentionally omitted. Lane maps are a HYPOTHESIS verified by examples/gfx1250/wmma_probe.py. MEMORY: gfx1250 HAS async global->LDS DMA (its own GFX12 family: global_load_async_to_lds_b128 + s_wait_asynccnt -- NOT the gfx9 buffer_load_lds/global_load_lds, which do not select), so has_async_global_lds=true (GPU-validated via the DTLA path). It also HAS a hardware transpose-LDS read, ds_load_tr16_b128 (GPU-validated via compute_pv_dstr). The has_async_lds and has_ds_read_tr flags stay false on purpose: in this catalog they denote the gfx9/gfx950 ds_read_*_tr_* / async-LDS *ABI* used to admit the gfx950 MFMA tiled builder (attention_arch.py), which gfx1250 does NOT have -- its async/transpose use distinct GFX12 opcodes gated directly in the ISA backend, not via these MFMA-pipeline bits. has_tdm=false: TDM not verified on this part.",
      "family": "cdna",
      "target_family": "gfx12_cdna",
      "matrix_path": "wmma",
      "has_mfma": false,
      "has_wmma": true,
      "waitcnt_model": "split_gfx1250",
      "barrier_model": "split_named_cluster",
      "requires_shader_end_padding": true,
      "virtual_address_bits": 57,
      "wgp_cache_lds_shared": true,
      "wave_size": 32,
      "lds_capacity_bytes": 163840,
      "vmcnt_bits": 6,
      "memory": {
        "has_async_lds": false,
        "has_async_global_lds": true,
        "has_ds_read_tr": false,
        "has_tdm": false,
        "buffer_load_max_dwords": 4
      },
      "limits": {
        "max_threads_per_block": 1024,
        "vgprs": 256,
        "agprs": 0,
        "sgprs": 106
      },
      "mma": [
        {"family": "wmma", "a": "fp16", "b": "fp16", "c": "fp32", "m": 16, "n": 16, "k": 32, "op_id": "wmma_gfx1250_f32_16x16x32_f16"},
        {"family": "wmma", "a": "bf16", "b": "bf16", "c": "fp32", "m": 16, "n": 16, "k": 32, "op_id": "wmma_gfx1250_f32_16x16x32_bf16"},
        {"family": "wmma", "a": "fp8", "b": "fp8", "c": "fp32", "m": 16, "n": 16, "k": 64, "op_id": "wmma_gfx1250_f32_16x16x64_fp8_fp8"},
        {"family": "wmma", "a": "fp8", "b": "bf8", "c": "fp32", "m": 16, "n": 16, "k": 64, "op_id": "wmma_gfx1250_f32_16x16x64_fp8_bf8"},
        {"family": "wmma", "a": "bf8", "b": "fp8", "c": "fp32", "m": 16, "n": 16, "k": 64, "op_id": "wmma_gfx1250_f32_16x16x64_bf8_fp8"},
        {"family": "wmma", "a": "bf8", "b": "bf8", "c": "fp32", "m": 16, "n": 16, "k": 64, "op_id": "wmma_gfx1250_f32_16x16x64_bf8_bf8"}
      ]
    },
